{"tid":986464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【拍劇當試煉】跟圈外追求者有好開始 唐詩詠唔排除閃婚 ","createTime":"2019-01-18T12:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T15:15:14.000Z","uid":221463,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"533a9179fdd5471045456595786e8ed18e21c030","tid":986464,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"想閃婚，唐姨應該好心急啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【今日直撃】唐詩詠在除夕倒數活動上承認有圈外追求者，今日出席商場活動時即被追問進展如何？她說：「食吓飯，都OK。（有無機會發展？）每個人都有機會，我唔可以放棄這些機會，起碼大家傾到偈、食到飯。（算是好開始？）係，係個好開始。（要觀察多久？）唔知，我嚟緊開劇，是個好好&hellip;試煉，我嘅時間表不是每個人都接受到，可能人哋接受唔到呢？（希望今年「脫單」？）又無一個期限畀自己&hellip;（會否閃婚？）有機會﹗（畀3個月時間對方？）驚嚇親人&hellip;，我唔止，要拍5個月，是好大嘅試驗﹗」<br />\n提到上年聖誕節在Ig上載4人合照，並留言話有3個人妻，唐詩詠解釋是講當中已婚的圈外女仔、黃翠如及C君的女友，並不是講自己，坦言自己會努力的。<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1547806424525&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20190118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1547806424525%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20190118&d=Ufld9kdgf6plUZmBe%2FWzNjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d39068f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1547806424525%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20190118&h=92972296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1547806424525&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20190118</a>"},{"pid":"fdd533dac54c3d6d9aa5c53241e78d5d8738e2d4","tid":986464,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"停經未"},{"pid":"c58c10a787b0157d5516b9838a6234c2441e0440","tid":986464,"uid":221463,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fdd533dac54c3d6d9aa5c53241e78d5d8738e2d4","tid":986464,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"停經未"},"citedBy":0,"replyT